column1: A working dinner tonight with Prime Minister Abe of Japan, and his representatives, at the Winter White House (Mar-a-Lago). Very good talks!
I am so proud of my daughter Ivanka. To be abused and treated so badly by the media, and to still hold her head so high, is truly wonderful!
Melania and I are hosting Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe and Mrs․ Abe at Mar-a-Lago in Palm Beach, Fla. They are a wonderful couple!

I am reading that the great border WALL will cost more than the government originally thought, but I have not gotten involved in the design or negotiations yet. When I do, just like with the F-35 FighterJet or the Air Force One Program, price will come WAY DOWN!
Our legal system is broken! "77% of refugees allowed into U․S․ since travel reprieve hail from seven suspect countries." (WT) SO DANGEROUS!
